summary: (Managing) Director that builds well-functioning teams and makes things happen. Experience within strategy development, sales management (B2B, export & retail), marketing management and reorganization in the medical devices and construction sectors. Worked in diverse large projects, such as ISO 9001, ISO13485 and MDR implementation, ERP (SAP, Axapta) implementation, Fleet Management and store network development. Speaks and writes fluent Dutch, English and Swedish. Understands French good, speaking on intermediate level.
